    "Their work does not delve into the motivations behind these AI-driven cyberattacks, their broader societal impact, or the variety of mitigation strategies beyond technological countermeasures.",
    "This leaves a gap in understanding the multidimensional influences and consequences of AI-driven cyberattacks.",
